##DESCRIPTION
##  Linear inequalities with absolute value
##ENDDESCRIPTION

## KEYWORDS('linear', 'inequality', 'absolute value')

## DBsubject('Algebra') 
## BookTitle('Equations and Inequalities')
## DBchapter('Absolute Value') 
## Date('Spring 2012')
